episodes.title: Las Vegas News | 7@7 PM for Friday, January 30, 2026
episodes.description: A verdict is reached in the case of the 'Dancing with Wolves' actor accused of sexual assault, Southern Nevada food pantries saw a surge in need last year, a specialized hospital in Henderson is the first of its kind in Nevada and more on 7@7.

episodes.title: Verdict in Nathan Chasing Horse case
episodes.description: A verdict has been reached in the sexual assault trial of alleged cult leader Nathan Chasing Horse in Las Vegas.
